<li>Republicans and Democrats will host county assemblies this weekend and next. Check with your local party for times and locations. The Denver Democratic Party will also hold state House and Senate district assemblies on Saturday via Zoom. You can watch the assembly <a target="_blank"  href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3kSu9yNMalo">here</a>.</li>
</ul>

